        ----------
        acceleration_limit : numpy.ndarray, shape (N,), dtype=float64
            Acceleration limits [rad/s²].
        
        Returns
        -------
        JointImpedanceControlCommandBuilder
            Self reference for method chaining.
        
        Notes
        -----
        - Vector length :math:`N` must match the component DOF.
